      "title": "Numbered Discourses 10 ",
      "expandable": false
    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:2.1",
          "pli": "“Kimatthiyāni, bhante, kusalāni sīlāni kimānisaṃsānī”ti? ",
          "en": "“Sir, what is the purpose and benefit of skillful ethics?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:2.2",
          "pli": "“Avippaṭisāratthāni kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsānī”ti. ",
          "en": "“Ānanda, having no regrets is the purpose and benefit of skillful ethics.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:3.1",
          "pli": "“Avippaṭisāro pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of having no regrets?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:3.2",
          "pli": "“Avippaṭisāro kho, ānanda, pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso”ti. ",
          "en": "“Joy is the purpose and benefit of having no regrets.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:4.1",
          "pli": "“Pāmojjaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsan”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of joy?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:4.2",
          "pli": "“Pāmojjaṃ kho, ānanda, pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsan”ti. ",
          "en": "“Rapture …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:5.1",
          "pli": "“Pīti pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of rapture?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:5.2",
          "pli": "“Pīti kho, ānanda, passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā”ti. ",
          "en": "“Tranquility …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:6.1",
          "pli": "“Passaddhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of tranquility?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:6.2",
          "pli": "“Passaddhi kho, ānanda, sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā”ti. ",
          "en": "“Bliss …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:7.1",
          "pli": "“Sukhaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsan”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of bliss?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:7.2",
          "pli": "“Sukhaṃ kho, ānanda, samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsan”ti. ",
          "en": "“Immersion …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:8.1",
          "pli": "“Samādhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of immersion?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:8.2",
          "pli": "“Samādhi kho, ānanda, yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso”ti. ",
          "en": "“Truly knowing and seeing …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:9.1",
          "pli": "“Yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsan”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of truly knowing and seeing?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:9.2",
          "pli": "“Yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ kho, ānanda, nibbidāvirāgatthaṃ nibbidāvirāgānisaṃsan”ti. ",
          "en": "“Disillusionment and dispassion …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:10.1",
          "pli": "“Nibbidāvirāgo pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso”ti? ",
          "en": "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of disillusionment and dispassion?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:10.2",
          "pli": "“Nibbidāvirāgo kho, ānanda, vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso. ",
          "en": "“Knowledge and vision of freedom is the purpose and benefit of disillusionment and dispassion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.1",
          "pli": "Iti kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisāratthāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsāni; ",
          "en": "So, Ānanda, the purpose and benefit of skillful ethics is not having regrets. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.2",
          "pli": "avippaṭisāro pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso; ",
          "en": "Joy is the purpose and benefit of not having regrets. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.3",
          "pli": "pāmojjaṃ pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsaṃ; ",
          "en": "Rapture is the purpose and benefit of joy. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.4",
          "pli": "pīti passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā; ",
          "en": "Tranquility is the purpose and benefit of rapture. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.5",
          "pli": "passaddhi sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā; ",
          "en": "Bliss is the purpose and benefit of tranquility. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.6",
          "pli": "sukhaṃ samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsaṃ; ",
          "en": "Immersion is the purpose and benefit of bliss. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.7",
          "pli": "samādhi yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso; ",
          "en": "Truly knowing and seeing is the purpose and benefit of immersion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.8",
          "pli": "yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ nibbidāvirāgatthaṃ nibbidāvirāgānisaṃsaṃ; ",
          "en": "Disillusionment and dispassion is the purpose and benefit of truly knowing and seeing. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.9",
          "pli": "nibbidāvirāgo vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso. ",
          "en": "Knowledge and vision of freedom is the purpose and benefit of disillusionment and dispassion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.10",
          "pli": "Iti kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni anupubbena aggāya parentī”ti. ",
          "en": "So, Ānanda, skillful ethics progressively lead up to the highest.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an10.1:11.11",
          "pli": "Paṭhamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
